(One word Booker T and the Alliance are a bunch of no-talent losers: 
spinerooni.)

Otyebis Military:



The fleshlings payed no attnetion to the Cybertronians, completing loading up 
the Autobots, sealing the hatch, and powering engines.

---

"If you leave," a soldier said to Daemos, "and the matches start and you 
aren't here, you won't be allowed back in."

---

Pointing to four hatches with the Maximals' names on them, Firearm, etc, one 
of the seven escorts said: "Hurry up rustbuckets."
